//api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte/labels/bug","name":"bug","color":"d73a4a","default":true,"description":"Something isn't working"},{"id":3145518949,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwzMTQ1NTE4OTQ5","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte/labels/triage","name":"triage","color":"A33977","default":false,"description":"Awaiting triage by a project member"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2026-05-08T15:01:50Z","updated_at":"2026-05-08T16:12:53Z","closed_at":"2026-05-08T15:34:46Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Describe the bug\n\nYesterday, I wanted to make changes to a project I made 3 months ago. The project was created with `6.1.2` , while trying to get the project running I ran `bun install` which updated vite-plugin-svelte to `7.1.2` .\n\nI then ran `bun run dev` only to see vite output error `No loader is configured for \".svelte\" files` then quits, i tried to remedy the solution yesterday . I couldn't.\n\nToday after over 3 hours and 3 llms, claude told me to look at my `package.json`, lo and behold there is a change vite-plugin-svelte has been updated to `7.1.2` .\n\nI downgraded the project to `6.1.2` , vite finally ran.\n\nI don't know if this is an issue, i searched everywhere and did not see any note saying v7 has a breaking change so i decided to create this issue.\n\nNOTE: updating vite to `7.3.3` did not fix it.\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f480c790-d5f5-440e-9f6d-0f0aaf8a98c7\n\n### Reproduction URL\n\nhttps://github.com/daviddanielng/frontend-reproduction\n\n### Reproduction\n\n1. clone repo\n2.  run `bun install`\n3. check that vite-plugin-svelte is at `6.1.2`, if it is not then run `bun add -d @sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte@^6.1.2`\n4. run `bun run dev` \n5. works\n6. run `bun add -d @sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte@^7.1.2` \n7. then run `bun run dev`\n8. output a long list of error all saying ` [ERROR] No loader is configured for \".svelte\" files` \n\n### Logs\n\n```shell\ntoo large.\n```\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\nSystem:\n    OS: Linux 6.12 Debian GNU/Linux 13 (trixie) 13 (trixie)\n    CPU: (4) x64 Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-6200U CPU @ 2.30GHz\n    Memory: 2.04 GB / 7.63 GB\n    Container: Yes\n    Shell: 5.2.37 - /bin/bash\n  Binaries:\n    Node: 24.14.1 - /home/daniel/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.1/bin/node\n    npm: 11.11.0 - /home/daniel/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.1/bin/npm\n    bun: 1.3.10 - /home/daniel/.bun/bin/bun\n  Browsers:\n    Chrome: 147.0.7727.55\n    Firefox: 140.9.0esr\n    Firefox Developer Edition: 140.9.0esr\n  npmPackages:\n    @sveltejs/adapter-auto: ^7.0.0 => 7.0.1 \n    @sveltejs/adapter-static: ^3.0.10 => 3.0.10 \n    @sveltejs/kit: ^2.49.1 => 2.59.1 \n    @sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte: ^7.1.2 => 7.1.2 \n    svelte: ^5.45.6 => 5.55.5 \n    vite: 7.3.3 => 7.3.3\n```","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte/issues/1346/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte/issues/1346/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"not_planned","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/events","html_url":"https://github.com/joshuafolkken/joshua