XSS via Insecure Promise Serialization in hydratable (vulnerable: `>= 5.46.0, <= 5.55.6`)\n- **Alert #47** — Svelte SSR vulnerable to cross-site scripting via spread attributes (vulnerable: `<= 5.55.6`)\n- **Alert #48** — Svelte Vulnerable to XSS via DOM Clobbering of Internal Framework State (vulnerable: `<= 5.55.6`)\n\nAll three are fixed in svelte 5.55.7.\n\n## Expected Result\n\n- `svelte` direct dep bumped to `^5.55.7`\n- Transitive resolutions also forced to `>=5.55.7` via a `pnpm.overrides` entry (so any dep pulling svelte through resolves the security fix)\n- `devalue` (used by SvelteKit for SSR serialization, implicated in alert #46) pinned to `^5.8.1`\n- `pnpm.overrides` tidied: drop entries that are no longer needed (`undici`, `drizzle-orm`, `@sveltejs/kit`, `uuid`) and simplify range formats for `esbuild` / `cookie`\n- `packageManager` pnpm patch bump: 11.1.1 → 11.1.2\n- All Dependabot alerts close; CI green\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `svelte` resolved version `>= 5.55.7` everywhere in the lockfile\n- [ ] `devalue` resolved version `>= 5.8.1`\n- [ ] `pnpm.overrides` reflects the refactor; no regressions on dropped overrides\n- [ ] `pnpm install` succeeds with no peer-dep errors\n- [ ] Existing unit (`pnpm josh test:unit`) + E2E (`pnpm josh test`) suites pass\n- [ ] Dependabot alerts #46, #47, #48 auto-close after merge","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/joshuafolkken/joshuafolkken-com/issues/592/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/language-tools/issues/3028","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/language-tools","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/language-tools/issues/3028/labels{/name}","comment